enhanced_by.reason: buildJSONString can generate the JSON string input required by getJSONStringValue.
addKeyValue can modify the JSON object to include the key-value pair needed for getJSONStringValue.
getJSONIntValue should be invoked before getJSONStringValue if both methods are used in the same test to ensure the JSON object is correctly parsed.
pullValue can be used to remove a key from the JSON object before invoking getJSONStringValue to test edge cases.
